{
  "stem": "11771.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was running after her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About halfway to Lida, she told me the whole story and she gave me a name, where to contact in Voranava-- Polish guy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I came-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I came the same night to Voranava, because I couldn't get back to Radun, because they, they warned me they don't want to see me anymore in Radun.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No question about to register me, because they got to register me on a false name that I am not Radun resident.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Otherwise, no Jew is allowed to, to take me in and to [INAUDIBLE] over sleep.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I got an opportunity to go to Radun-- and I have an address and a name-- to a Polish man.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was in the underground, and probably Judy got a connection with him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I came-- when I went to Voranava-- same night, they took her away afternoon-- it was afternoon, a Sunday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took her away to Lida, and I set on my way to Voranava.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The way was the only lucky thing with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've got a very good sense of directions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it wasn't any problem to get to the point where I point out myself, not to ask.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the minute I ask somebody, I discover myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- but it was hard to find my-- the street where he is, and it was at night.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I got in [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the first house with not knowing this is a Jewish-- people live here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knock on the window.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And, who is there?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I say, ah, a Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw already, it was Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had the-- they asked me, I saw him.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
